From the choir to the altar, you sit behind the pews in the congregation. Observing the monotony...actually dozing off. Your lashes begin to fall as drift into your subconscious realm.  
Your 3rd eye is open. A spiritual "Call" within awakens your soul, urging you to find your higher purpose. Fulfill your role.

Soul Full is an upbeat antique song with gospel vibes made to inspire Shadow Work. What is Shadow work? The spiritual practice of freeing your inner truth. Becoming aware of your truth can allow you to understand the subconscious patterns that shape your conscious state. Practices such as Tarot, art, journaling, dream work, meditation, and music therapy are some of the many spiritual tools that release blockages, provide clarity, and heal.
